[{"id": 603011, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 502, "ruku": 438, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4511, "text": "Ha mim."}, {"id": 603012, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 502, "ruku": 438, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4512, "text": "Kitab\u0131n indirili\u015fi aziz, hakim olan Allah taraf\u0131ndand\u0131r."}, {"id": 603013, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 502, "ruku": 438, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4513, "text": "Biz g\u00f6kleri, yeri ve ikisi aras\u0131nda bulunanlar\u0131 (bo\u015f yere de\u011fil), ancak ger\u00e7ek ile ve belli bir s\u00fcreye g\u00f6re yaratt\u0131k. \u0130nkar edenler, uyar\u0131ld\u0131klar\u0131 \u015feyden y\u00fcz \u00e7evirmektedirler."}, {"id": 603014, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 502, "ruku": 438, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4514, "text": "De ki: \"Allah'tan ba\u015fka yalvard\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131z\u0131 g\u00f6rd\u00fcn\u00fcz m\u00fc? Bana g\u00f6sterin, onlar yerden neyi yaratt\u0131lar? Yoksa g\u00f6kler(in yarat\u0131l\u0131\u015f\u0131n)da onlar\u0131n bir ortakl\u0131\u011f\u0131 m\u0131 var? E\u011fer do\u011fru iseniz bundan \u00f6nce (inmi\u015f olan) bir Kitap, yahut bir bilgi kal\u0131nt\u0131s\u0131 getirin.\""}, {"id": 603015, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 502, "ruku": 438, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4515, "text": "Allah'\u0131 b\u0131rak\u0131p da k\u0131yamet g\u00fcn\u00fcne kadar kendisine cevap veremeyecek \u015feylere yalvarandan daha sap\u0131k kim olabilir? Oysa onlar, bunlar\u0131n yalvard\u0131klar\u0131ndan habersizdirler."}, {"id": 603017, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 503, "ruku": 438, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4516, "text": "\u0130nsanlar (Y\u00fcce Divana) topland\u0131klar\u0131 g\u00fcn, (tapt\u0131klar\u0131 tanr\u0131lar) onlara d\u00fc\u015fman olurlar ve onlar\u0131n, kendilerine tapmalar\u0131n\u0131 tan\u0131mazlar."}, {"id": 603018, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 503, "ruku": 438, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4517, "text": "Onlara a\u00e7\u0131k a\u00e7\u0131k ayetlerimiz okundu\u011fu zaman kendilerine gelen hakk\u0131 inkar edenler: \"Bu, apa\u00e7\u0131k bir b\u00fcy\u00fcd\u00fcr\" dediler."}, {"id": 603019, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 503, "ruku": 438, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4518, "text": "Yoksa \"Onu uydurdu\" mu diyorlar? De ki: \"E\u011fer ben onu uydurmu\u015fsam, Allah'tan gelecek cezaya kar\u015f\u0131 sizin bana hi\u00e7bir yarar\u0131n\u0131z olmaz. O, sizin yapt\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131z ta\u015fk\u0131nl\u0131\u011f\u0131 daha iyi bilir. Benimle sizin aran\u0131zda O'nun \u015fahid olmas\u0131 yeter. O, ba\u011f\u0131\u015flayan, esirgeyendir."}, {"id": 603020, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 503, "ruku": 438, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4519, "text": "De ki: \"Ben t\u00fcredi bir el\u00e7i de\u011filim. Bana ve size ne yap\u0131laca\u011f\u0131n\u0131 da bilmem. Ben sadece bana vahyedilene uyuyorum ve ben apa\u00e7\u0131k bir uyar\u0131c\u0131dan ba\u015fka bir \u015fey de\u011filim.\""}, {"id": 603021, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 503, "ruku": 438, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4520, "text": "De ki: \"Hi\u00e7 d\u00fc\u015f\u00fcnd\u00fcn\u00fcz m\u00fc: E\u011fer bu (Kur'an) Allah kat\u0131ndan oldu\u011fu halde siz onu tan\u0131mam\u0131\u015fsan\u0131z; \u0130srail o\u011fullar\u0131ndan bir \u015fahid de bunun benzerini (Tevrat'ta) g\u00f6r\u00fcp inand\u0131\u011f\u0131 halde siz (inanma\u011fa) tenezz\u00fcl etmemi\u015fseniz (durumunuz nice olur)? Allah, zalim bir toplumu do\u011fru yola iletmez."}, {"id": 603022, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 503, "ruku": 439, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4521, "text": "\u0130nkar edenler, inananlar i\u00e7in \"(Muhammed'in getirdi\u011fi) iyi bir \u015fey olsayd\u0131 (\u015fu zavall\u0131 ki\u015filer) ona inanmada bizi ge\u00e7emezlerdi, (biz onlardan \u00f6nce inan\u0131rd\u0131k) dediler. Onlar, onun g\u00f6sterdi\u011fi do\u011fru yola eremediklerinden: \"Bu eski bir yaland\u0131r,\" diyeceklerdir."}, {"id": 603023, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 503, "ruku": 439, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4522, "text": "Ondan \u00f6nce de \u00f6nder ve rahmet olarak Musa'n\u0131n Kitab\u0131 vard\u0131r. Bu da (\u015firk ile) kendilerine yaz\u0131k edenleri uyarmak, g\u00fczel davrananlar\u0131 m\u00fcjdelemek i\u00e7in Arap diliyle indirilmi\u015f (kendinden \u00f6nceki Kitab\u0131) do\u011frulayan Kitapt\u0131r."}, {"id": 603024, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 503, "ruku": 439, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4523, "text": "Rabbimiz Allah't\u0131r deyip sonra do\u011fru olanlar, onlara korku yoktur ve onlar \u00fcz\u00fclmeyeceklerdir."}, {"id": 603025, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 503, "ruku": 439, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4524, "text": "Onlar cennet halk\u0131d\u0131r, yapt\u0131klar\u0131na kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131k orada ebedi kalacaklard\u0131r."}, {"id": 603026, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 504, "ruku": 439, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4525, "text": "Biz insana, ana babas\u0131na iyilik etmesini tavsiye ettik. Anas\u0131 onu zahmetle ta\u015f\u0131d\u0131 ve zahmetle do\u011furdu. (Ana karn\u0131nda) Ta\u015f\u0131nmas\u0131 ile s\u00fctten kesilmesi otuz ay s\u00fcrd\u00fc. Nihayet (insan) g\u00fc\u00e7l\u00fc \u00e7a\u011f\u0131na erip k\u0131rk ya\u015f\u0131na var\u0131nca: \"Ya Rabbi dedi, beni, bana ve anama, babama verdi\u011fin ni'mete \u015f\u00fckretme\u011fe, raz\u0131 olaca\u011f\u0131n yararl\u0131 i\u015fler yapma\u011fa sevk eyle. Benim i\u00e7in z\u00fcrriyetim i\u00e7inde de salah\u0131 devam ettir (benden gelecek olanlar\u0131 da iyi insanlar yap). Ben sana y\u00fcz tuttum ve ben (sana) teslim olanlardan\u0131m."}, {"id": 603027, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 504, "ruku": 439, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4526, "text": "Onlar \u00f6yle ki\u015filerdir ki, yapt\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131n en iyisini onlardan kabul ederiz ve onlar\u0131n k\u00f6t\u00fcl\u00fcklerinden ge\u00e7eriz, cennet halk\u0131 aras\u0131ndad\u0131rlar. Bu, (d\u00fcnyada) kendilerine s\u00f6ylenen do\u011fru s\u00f6z(\u00fcn ger\u00e7ekle\u015fmesi)dir."}, {"id": 603028, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 504, "ruku": 439, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4527, "text": "Fakat o kimse ki anas\u0131na, babas\u0131na: \"\u00d6f size, benden \u00f6nce nice nesiller gelip ge\u00e7mi\u015f, (kimse geri gelmemi\u015f) iken siz benim (diriltilip) \u00e7\u0131kar\u0131laca\u011f\u0131m\u0131 m\u0131 bana va'dediyor(beni bununla m\u0131 tehdidediyor)sunuz?\" dedi. Onlarsa Allah'a s\u0131\u011f\u0131narak: \"Yaz\u0131k sana, (etme, gel) inan; Allah'\u0131n s\u00f6z\u00fc ger\u00e7ektir\" derken o: \"Bu, eskilerin masallar\u0131ndan ba\u015fka bir \u015fey de\u011fildir.\" der."}, {"id": 603029, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 504, "ruku": 439, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4528, "text": "\u0130\u015fte onlar da kendilerine (azab) s\u00f6z(\u00fc) gerekli olmu\u015f kimselerdir. Kendilerinden \u00f6nce ge\u00e7en cin ve insan topluluklar\u0131 aras\u0131nda (azab\u0131n i\u00e7inde) bulunacaklard\u0131r. Ger\u00e7ekten onlar, ziyana u\u011frayanlard\u0131r."}, {"id": 603030, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 504, "ruku": 439, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4529, "text": "Her birinin (inananlar\u0131n ve inanmayanlar\u0131n) yapt\u0131klar\u0131 i\u015flerden dereceleri vard\u0131r. Allah, onlara yapt\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131n kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 tam verir; kendilerine hi\u00e7 haks\u0131zl\u0131k edilmez."}, {"id": 603031, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 504, "ruku": 439, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4530, "text": "\u0130nkar edenler ate\u015fe sunulacaklar\u0131 g\u00fcn, (kendilerine denir ki): \"D\u00fcnya hayat\u0131n\u0131zda b\u00fct\u00fcn g\u00fczel \u015feylerinizi zayi ettiniz; (orada) bunlarla sefa s\u00fcr\u00fcp bunlar\u0131 t\u00fckettiniz (buras\u0131 i\u00e7in hi\u00e7bir \u015fey b\u0131rakmad\u0131n\u0131z). Yery\u00fcz\u00fcnde haks\u0131z yere b\u00fcy\u00fckl\u00fck taslaman\u0131zdan ve yoldan \u00e7\u0131kman\u0131zdan \u00f6t\u00fcr\u00fc bug\u00fcn, al\u00e7alt\u0131c\u0131 bir azab ile cezaland\u0131r\u0131lacaks\u0131n\u0131z.\""}, {"id": 603032, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 505, "ruku": 440, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4531, "text": "Ad'\u0131n karde\u015fini (Hud'u) an: Ah\u00c6af'taki kavmini uyarm\u0131\u015ft\u0131. Onun \u00f6n\u00fcnden ve ard\u0131ndan nice uyar\u0131c\u0131lar da gelip ge\u00e7ti (demi\u015fti ki): \"Allah'tan ba\u015fkas\u0131na kulluk etmeyin; ben sizin, b\u00fcy\u00fck bir g\u00fcn\u00fcn azab\u0131na u\u011framan\u0131zdan korkuyorum.\""}, {"id": 603033, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 505, "ruku": 440, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4532, "text": "Dediler: \"Sen bizi tanr\u0131lar\u0131m\u0131zdan \u00e7evirmek i\u00e7in mi geldin? Do\u011frulardan isen bizi tehdidetti\u011fin \u015feyi bize getir.\""}, {"id": 603034, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 505, "ruku": 440, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4533, "text": "Dedi: \"(Azab\u0131n ne zaman gelece\u011fine dair) Bilgi, ancak Allah kat\u0131ndad\u0131r. Ben, tebli\u011f g\u00f6revlendirildi\u011fim mesaj\u0131 size duyuruyorum; fakat sizi cahillik eden bir kavim g\u00f6r\u00fcyorum.\""}, {"id": 603035, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 505, "ruku": 440, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4534, "text": "Nihayet azab\u0131n (ufukta) geni\u015f bir bulut halinde vadilerine do\u011fru geldi\u011fini g\u00f6r\u00fcnce: \"Bu, bize ya\u011fmur ya\u011fd\u0131racak bir buluttur\" dediler. Hay\u0131r, o sizin acele gelmesini istedi\u011finiz \u015fey, i\u00e7inde ac\u0131 azab bulunan bir r\u00fczgard\u0131r."}, {"id": 603036, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 505, "ruku": 440, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4535, "text": "Rabbinin emriyle her \u015feyi y\u0131kar, mahveder. Derken onlar o hale geldiler ki konutlar\u0131ndan ba\u015fka bir \u015fey g\u00f6r\u00fclmez oldu. \u0130\u015fte biz, su\u00e7 i\u015fleyen toplumu b\u00f6yle cezaland\u0131r\u0131r\u0131z."}, {"id": 603037, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 505, "ruku": 440, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4536, "text": "Onlara size vermedi\u011fimiz servet ve kuvveti vermi\u015ftik, onlara kulaklar, g\u00f6zler ve g\u00f6n\u00fcller yaratm\u0131\u015ft\u0131k. Fakat ne kulaklar\u0131, ne g\u00f6zleri ne de g\u00f6n\u00fclleri kendilerine bir yarar sa\u011flad\u0131. Zira (d\u00fc\u015f\u00fcn\u00fcp ibret alm\u0131yorlar, tersine) bile bile Allah'\u0131n ayetlerini inkar ediyorlard\u0131. Ve alay edip durduklar\u0131 \u015fey, kendilerini ku\u015fat\u0131verdi."}, {"id": 603038, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 505, "ruku": 441, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4537, "text": "Andolsun, biz \u00e7evrenizdeki kentleri de yok ettik ve belki (k\u00fcf\u00fcrlerinden) d\u00f6nerler diye ayetleri tekrar tekrar a\u00e7\u0131klad\u0131k."}, {"id": 603039, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 505, "ruku": 441, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4538, "text": "Allah'tan ba\u015fka, kendilerine (Allah yan\u0131nda) yak\u0131nl\u0131k sa\u011flamak i\u00e7in tanr\u0131 edindikleri \u015feyler, kendilerine yard\u0131m etselerdi ya! Hay\u0131r, (tanr\u0131lar\u0131), onlardan kaybolup gittiler. \u0130\u015fte onlar\u0131n yalanlar\u0131 ve uydurmalar\u0131 budur."}, {"id": 603040, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 506, "ruku": 441, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4539, "text": "Bir zaman, cinlerden bir toplulu\u011fu Kur'an dinlemek \u00fczere sana y\u00f6neltmi\u015ftik. Ona geldiklerinde (birbirlerine): \"Susun, (dinleyin)\" dediler. (Okuma) Bitirilince de uyar\u0131c\u0131lar olarak kavimlerine d\u00f6nd\u00fcler:"}, {"id": 603041, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 506, "ruku": 441, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4540, "text": "Ey kavmimiz, dediler, biz Musa'dan sonra indirilen, kendinden \u00f6ncekini do\u011frulayan, ger\u00e7e\u011fe ve do\u011fru yola g\u00f6t\u00fcren bir Kitap dinledik."}, {"id": 603042, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 506, "ruku": 441, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4541, "text": "Ey kavmimiz, Allah'\u0131n da'vet\u00e7isine uyun ve O'na inan\u0131n ki (Allah) g\u00fcnahlar\u0131n\u0131zdan bir k\u0131sm\u0131n\u0131 ba\u011f\u0131\u015flas\u0131n ve sizi, ac\u0131 azabdan korusun."}, {"id": 603043, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 506, "ruku": 441, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4542, "text": "Kim Allah'\u0131n da'vet\u00e7isine uymazsa, yery\u00fcz\u00fcnde (ba\u015f\u0131na inecek belaya) engel olamaz. Kendisinin O'ndan ba\u015fka velileri de olmaz. Onlar, apa\u00e7\u0131k bir sap\u0131kl\u0131k i\u00e7indedirler."}, {"id": 603044, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 506, "ruku": 441, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4543, "text": "G\u00f6kleri ve yeri yaratan, bunlar\u0131 yaratmakla yorulmayan Allah'\u0131n, \u00f6l\u00fcleri diriltme\u011fe de kadir oldu\u011funu g\u00f6rmediler mi? Evet O, her \u015feye kadirdir."}, {"id": 603045, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 506, "ruku": 441, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4544, "text": "\u0130nkar edenler ate\u015fe sunulacaklar\u0131 g\u00fcn (Allah onlara): \"(Nas\u0131l), Bu ger\u00e7ek de\u011fil miymi\u015f?\" (der); \"Evet Rabbimiz hakk\u0131 i\u00e7in (ger\u00e7ekmi\u015f)\" derler. \"\u00d6yleyse inkar etmenizden dolay\u0131 azab\u0131 tad\u0131n\" der."}, {"id": 603046, "identifier": "tr.ates", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 506, "ruku": 441, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "S\u00fcleyman Ate\u015f", "transelator_en_name": "Suleyman Ates", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4545, "text": "O halde sen de, azim (ve irade) sahibi el\u00e7ilerin sabrettikleri gibi sabret. O (nank\u00f6r)ler i\u00e7in acele etme. Onlar, tehdidedildikleri azab\u0131 g\u00f6rd\u00fckleri g\u00fcn, sanki g\u00fcnd\u00fcz\u00fcn sadece bir sa'ati kadar ya\u015fam\u0131\u015f gibi olurlar. (Bu) Bir duyurudur. Yoldan \u00e7\u0131km\u0131\u015f topluluktan ba\u015fkas\u0131 m\u0131 helak edilecektir?"}]